snippet.title: Don’t Starve: Newhome | A New Mysterious Adventure (Story Trailer)
snippet.description:
A mysterious new survival adventure is on the way! Don’t Starve: Newhome is a multiplayer evolution of the beloved franchise. Meet new characters, odd creatures and jump into online co-op or a quick pick up and play session.  Your “Newhome” is coming soon to iOS and Android!

Follow us for news and updates!
